{
  "stem": "11611.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had to sit in the consular office for three days in order to get her across the border.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, she became a US citizen promptly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yup.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came straight home and I thought I was really in for it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd have to go into private practice, which was no part of my thinking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was in touch with Charlie Lyon, whom I mentioned at Nuremberg, who was a tax lawyer by background, with a rather well-known Washington firm.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, why don't you go into tax practice?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, don't be crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never even took a tax course in law school-- which I didn't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which, at Harvard, was unusual, because 95%, 99% of the class took tax courses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not me, because I was never going to go anywhere near it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I haven't even filled in a tax return up to that point, as far as I can remember.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, I have some friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They might want to hire you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went up and talked to his friends and one of them had a commitment to write a book so he hired-- on taxes-- so he hired me basically to write a book on taxes.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we never wrote a book on taxes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I worked on one chapter and then I gradually got integrated into the tax practice itself, and then I was ruined for life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a tax lawyer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was with this relatively smaller firm for about a year or two, and then I was-- became an associative at Paul Weiss in New York.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Paul Weiss in New York, I went to Paul Weiss in Washington-- which was where Randolph Paul was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Randolph Paul was the Paul of Paul Weiss.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
